            <li><strong>Easy Onboarding:</strong> New to Arkavo? Our onboarding process guides you through setting up your account, choosing your preferences, and exploring the app's key features.</li>
            <li><strong>Account Recovery:</strong> If you ever need help recovering your account, our support team is here to assist you. We also offer an optional Arkavo account recovery service that securely stores your information in encrypted form, making it easier to regain access if needed.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4>Managing Your Account</h4>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Profile Management:</strong> Customize your profile settings, manage your data, and update your preferences through the app. If you need assistance, our Help Center offers guides on account management.</li>
            <li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> If you wish to download your data or transfer it to another service, our support team can help you with the process.</li>
