            <li><strong>Terms and Conditions:</strong> Please review our Terms and Conditions to understand the legal agreements governing your use of Arkavo. These are available in the app and on our website.</li>
            <li><strong>Safety Guidelines:</strong> We are committed to creating a safe and secure environment for all users. Please adhere to our safety guidelines and report any suspicious activity to our support team.</li>
        </ul>

